<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>프로젝트 등록 완료!</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4285f4, #34a853);
        color: #fff;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .wrapper {
        text-align: center;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        padding: 48px 40px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        max-width: 420px;
        width: calc(100% - 32px);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        font-size: 2.4rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      }

      p {
        margin: 0 0 24px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-size: 1rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
      }

      a {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 12px;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #202124;
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 999px;
        text-decoration: none;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(32, 33, 36, 0.2);
        transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
      }

      a:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(32, 33, 36, 0.28);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="wrapper">
      <h1><%= isEdit ? '프로젝트 수정 완료!' : '프로젝트 등록 완료!' %></h1>
      <p>
        <%= isEdit
          ? '프로젝트가 성공적으로 수정되었습니다.'
          : '새로운 프로젝트가 성공적으로 등록되었습니다.' %>
      </p>
      <a href="/projects/1">대쉬보드로 이동</a>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
